.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:2:title: "system skill advisor hooks codex lib: Code README"
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:3:description: "Code-facing README for .opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib."
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:5:  - "system-skill-advisor hooks/codex/lib"
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:9:# system skill advisor hooks codex lib
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:11:Runtime hook code that connects the skill to CLI event surfaces.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:19:This README documents the code-bearing folder `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib` so operators can understand its role without opening every source file first. It follows the sk-doc skill README structure while staying focused on code navigation.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:39:Start with `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/SKILL.md` for runtime routing and workflow boundaries.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:44:rg --files .opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:51:Load this folder through the owning skill workflow or MCP server entrypoint.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:87:User request: Check .opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib for sk-code and README coverage.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/hooks/codex/lib/README.md:99:| Verification command is unclear | Folder is a helper boundary | Use the nearest package or skill-level verification command. |
