.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:30:This playbook provides 29 deterministic scenarios across 9 categories validating the current `deep-loop-runtime` skill surface. Each scenario maps to one feature catalog entry and one dedicated scenario file with objective, prompt, execution steps, source anchors, and verdict criteria.
