.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/INSTALL_GUIDE.md:367:5. Smoke-test via the `advisor_recommend` MCP tool against three queries (`"memory save"`, `"code search"`, `"spec folder"`) and confirm top-3 picks are sane.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/INSTALL_GUIDE.md:369:The full runbook (snapshot + stop + override + restart + smoke test + rollback) is documented at [`002-jina-swap-and-reindex/evidence/swap-runbook.md`](../../<spec-folder>). The "Architecture Context" and "Half-wired state" sections are now historical — the half-wired state was closed by phase `004`.
