.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/handlers/skill-graph/README.md:15:`handlers/skill-graph/` owns the `mk_skill_advisor` MCP-facing handlers for the SQLite-backed skill graph. The handlers parse tool arguments, call skill graph libraries and return redacted JSON response envelopes.
