.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/handlers/README.md:18:`skill_advisor/handlers/` contains MCP tool handlers for advisor operations. The handlers are thin entrypoints that delegate recommendation, status, rebuild and validation behavior to library modules.
