.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:2:title: "System Skill Advisor MCP Server"
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:10:# System Skill Advisor MCP Server
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:12:> Standalone MCP runtime for skill recommendation routing, freshness tracking and skill graph relationship queries.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:18:`mcp_server/` owns the standalone `mk_skill_advisor` MCP server. It exposes 9 public tools across two surfaces: advisor routing (`advisor_*`) and skill graph queries (`skill_graph_*`).
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:23:- `tools/` defines tool descriptors and dispatches calls. `tools/index.ts:37-43` registers `TOOL_DEFINITIONS` with 4 advisor tools plus the spread of skill-graph tools.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:24:- `handlers/` owns orchestration for advisor tools (recommend, rebuild, status, validate) and skill-graph subhandlers (scan, query, status, validate, propagate_enhances).
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:25:- `lib/` carries the runtime helpers across 11 subdirectories: `scorer/`, `daemon/`, `freshness/`, `lifecycle/`, `derived/`, `compat/`, `auth/`, `corpus/`, `cross-skill-edges/`, `context/` and `shadow/`, plus several flat modules.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:26:- `database/skill-graph.sqlite` stores skill metadata, relationships and derived signals. Schema initialization and prepared queries live in `lib/skill-graph/skill-graph-db.ts` and `lib/skill-graph/skill-graph-queries.ts`.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:27:- Packet 013/009/011 moved the skill graph DB/query library and startup lifecycle under this package. Extraction is complete.
