.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:275:| `advisor_recommend` | Tool | Returns skill recommendations for a given prompt. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:278:| `advisor_validate` | Tool | Validates advisor configuration and routing bundle. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:279:| `skill_graph_scan` | Tool | Indexes or re-indexes skill metadata into SQLite. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:280:| `skill_graph_query` | Tool | Queries skill graph relationships (dependencies, enhances, hubs). |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:281:| `skill_graph_status` | Tool | Reports skill graph health and counts. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:282:| `skill_graph_validate` | Tool | Validates skill graph for schema drift, broken edges and cycles. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/README.md:283:| `skill_graph_propagate_enhances` | Tool | Detects and (opt-in) applies missing inbound enhance edges across skills. |
