.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:2:title: "Skill Advisor Tools: MCP Tool Descriptors"
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:3:description: "Tool descriptor modules for native advisor and skill graph MCP endpoints."
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:10:# Skill Advisor Tools: MCP Tool Descriptors
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:18:`mcp_server/tools/` contains MCP `ToolDefinition` descriptors for the standalone `mk_skill_advisor` surface. Each descriptor defines a tool name, prompt-safe description and JSON Schema input contract.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:22:- `advisor_recommend` routes prompts through the native advisor scorer.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:25:- `advisor_validate` runs the heavier advisor validation bundle after explicit confirmation.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:26:- `skill_graph_scan`, `skill_graph_query`, `skill_graph_status` and `skill_graph_validate` expose the advisor-owned skill graph MCP surface.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:36:+-- advisor-recommend.ts      # advisor_recommend descriptor
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:38:+-- advisor-validate.ts       # advisor_validate descriptor
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:40:+-- skill-graph-tools.ts      # skill_graph_* descriptors and dispatcher
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:52:| `advisor-recommend.ts` | Defines the `advisor_recommend` input schema and descriptor text. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:54:| `advisor-rebuild.ts` | Defines the explicit rebuild descriptor and optional `force` flag. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:57:| `skill-graph-tools.ts` | Defines `skill_graph_scan`, `skill_graph_query`, `skill_graph_status` and `skill_graph_validate`. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:91:| `advisorRecommendTool` | Descriptor | Registers `advisor_recommend`. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:94:| `advisorValidateTool` | Descriptor | Registers `advisor_validate`. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:95:| `skillGraphScanTool` | Descriptor | Registers `skill_graph_scan`. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:96:| `skillGraphQueryTool` | Descriptor | Registers `skill_graph_query`. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:97:| `skillGraphStatusTool` | Descriptor | Registers `skill_graph_status`. |
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tools/README.md:98:| `skillGraphValidateTool` | Descriptor | Registers `skill_graph_validate`. |
