.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/feature_catalog/04--scorer-fusion/06-weights-config.md:21:`lib/scorer/weights-config.ts` defines the canonical weights from `lib/scorer/lane-registry.ts`: `explicit_author: 0.42`, `lexical: 0.28`, `graph_causal: 0.13`, `derived_generated: 0.12`, `semantic_shadow: 0.05`. These values are surfaced through `advisor_status.laneWeights` and consumed by `lib/scorer/fusion.ts`.
