.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/hooks/skill_advisor_hook.md:66:- use `0.8 / 0.35` as the default prompt-time confidence/uncertainty routing thresholds unless a caller explicitly overrides the confidence threshold
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/hooks/skill_advisor_hook.md:69:Native `advisor_recommend` returns prompt-safe lane contribution metadata when `includeAttribution` is true. It does not return prompt-derived evidence snippets.
