.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/graph/skill_graph_extraction_plan.md:20:Records the current ownership state of `lib/skill-graph/` inside `system-skill-advisor` after extraction from `system-spec-kit`.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/graph/skill_graph_extraction_plan.md:24:- Checking whether skill graph code still needs migration.
