.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/changelog/v0.1.0.md:84:No migration required. Pre-1.0 preview: public tool ids (`advisor_recommend`, `advisor_rebuild`, `advisor_status`, `advisor_validate`, `skill_graph_*`) are stable. Existing configs that referenced `system_skill_advisor` should rename the entry to `mk_skill_advisor` and point `command`/`args` at `.opencode/bin/mk-skill-advisor-launcher.cjs`. The Python shim (`skill_advisor.py`) remains available. Set `SPECKIT_SKILL_ADVISOR_FORCE_LOCAL=1` to fall back to the legacy local scorer for diagnosis.
