.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/embedders/README.md:18:`lib/embedders/` is the advisor package's local adapter surface for skill-graph embeddings. It owns advisor database schema helpers and re-exports the canonical embedder registry from `@spec-kit/shared`.
