    23	 *   Symbols: identifiers used as function calls, e.g. `foo(...)` or `Foo.bar(...)`,
    24	 *     where the identifier is at least 4 chars.
    25	 *
    26	 * Common-name allowlist (always-real, never flagged): standard JS builtins,
    27	 * Node fs/path/crypto methods, common test-framework symbols.
